      "title": "SLFP to meet President for talks on National Govt \u2013 Sirisena",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); \u00a0The Sri Lanka Freedom Party will meet President Ranil Wickremesinghe for discussions on forming a national government, said Former President Maithripala Sirisena on Thursday (28).",
        "He told a media briefing that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party had continuously called for an all party government, however, that call has not been taken into consideration.",
        "SLFP to meet President for talks on National Govt \u2013 Sirisena",
        "Appropriate to call for elections \u2013 Maha Sangha tells elections Chief"
